title: "The Mall sank into the earth."
description: Jon, Jon and Tommy talk about Trump's inaugural address, the women's marches across the US and Sean Spicer's wonderful weekend. Then they're joined by Seth Meyers from "Late Night with Seth Meyers".
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
